# Assets Loans And Receivables Lease Financing Gross Total Amount

## identifier
de1016

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for the total gross loans and advances representing lease financing, it is reported net of unearned revenue and gross of provisions.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.LeaseFinancingGrossTotal.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.00
- period=instant
